Mint
================================================================================


Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mint is IRC Bot Pluggable Framework.


Require
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Tiarra

[Tiarra - IRC Proxy software](http://www.clovery.jp/tiarra/)

### RubyGems

1. net-irc
2. daemons


Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. start

        ./mintd start

2. restart

        ./mintd restart

3. stop

        ./mintd stop

4. config file change

        ./mintd start -- -c config.yaml

5. run on the top(not daemonize)

        ./mintd run

6. Usage

        ./mintd (run|start) -- -h
